{"id": 2575, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于未来城市长啥样，你觉得哪些思路不太对劲？", "description": "丹麦城市规划顾问 Jan Gehl 认为：“当代大都市，像是迪拜所意图实现的，是一种关于未来城市恶俗想象的大汇总。”", "record_count": 13429, "comment_count": 36, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181017112601Y6diCm0tKG7aBILN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-18T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4810, "title": "关于未来城市长啥样，你觉得哪些思路不太对劲？", "content": "关于未来城市长啥样，你觉得哪些思路不太对劲？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 304726, "content": "步行空间被挤占，陆地、天空和海都塞满更快的飞车", "image": "img/option/option/20181017113207FGJ9Q3KzM5g7ELY2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304728, "content": "城市分层，人们生活在空中/地下，地上变成垃圾堆", "image": "img/option/option/20181017153731vJQAGLMEs5PzYpcx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304730, "content": "城市外表被虚拟技术美化，不在乎真实建筑长什么样", "image": "img/option/option/20181017151046gnmwPB9ESv4hbLjD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304733, "content": "不关心邻居和社区，只展示自己的房间可以有多高科技", "image": "img/option/option/20181017113728iLWMwsPyu5JImfUS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304734, "content": "人类移民外星，地球城市成为流放犯人的监狱", "image": "img/option/option/20181017151239ehvA8EZ9xW7TuNPy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304736, "content": "虚拟眼镜下，所有的城市墙面都是logo和广告", "image": "img/option/option/20181017151530AdFqy69JZI4zUewC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304737, "content": "不再需要自己走，所有道路都自动移动", "image": "img/option/option/20181017114316bQR1VvF2HKOtS94l.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304747, "content": "所有建筑都联通，人类只生存在密闭的空调建筑里", "image": "img/option/option/20181017153213Mb5IQHg7k16cx8Pt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}